criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Has worked at current job for at least 12 months;

          2. Intensity of low back pain on Visual Analogue Scale (scale 0-10) at least two during
             the past 3 months.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Serious former back injury (fracture, surgery, disc protrusion);

          2. Pregnant;

          3. Other serious disease or symptoms that limit participation exercise defined by a
             physician.
